lemma red_ord: assumes "red F p q" shows "q \<prec>\<^sub>p p"
using assms
unfolding red_def
proof
fix f
assume "f \<in> F" and "\<exists>x. red_single p q f x"
then
obtain x where "red_single p q f x"
by auto
thus "q \<prec>\<^sub>p p"
by (rule red_single_ord)
qed
